(Primary/Social/Promotions)

- Smart  
Compose<https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AD-FnEytm9D6HW8hUFEcD6ebYJ1_kwTvjemM7nxjjyIU1_qDCcJHtMZUWsiS2Qta7xdo_903yJGr0DJMNCfLhf95Or-pcDFW2vIwYlLNLAR7cDq0xpPBvfpzhJtKCE8WhlRw5w>  
and Smart  
Reply<https://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AD-FnEwbvhp-tRmb6OKOI2OawFAEh4sgnL0eBj0iHvefBwwhFozsocuMlATn5FNj_3YdTaSyiNEm9rAvqpiStAs05IgkWjJqdZYjcE5vTHtWkQg3Krvx0hLkIEF_pFHZ-rz9kJA>  
