What do I need to do?

If you want to continue using the above features and more after January  
25th, 2021, you need to choose in Gmail settings to keep these features on.  
If you have already made your choices for these settings on either your  
mobile Gmail app or desktop, no further action is needed. You can change  
these options in Gmail settings at any time. Learn  
more<http://www.google.com/appserve/mkt/p/AD-FnExC3kjpqbhYLv2yBkasdhBpXv5ikJG8nN-VPgjQCD0OJbw4mzn0gwFr75Pc4tc5h3a9_FNG2hA5Fvm1XilYZ8sYySccBID82yWIfC2tM-uEl24TrVbvh9BnhLaY6h_j2D8>

